        <ab><lb n="1"/>sidhaṁ namo bhagavato saṁmasaṁbu<supplied reason="omitted">dha</supplied>sa dhātuvaraparigahitasa mahācetīye <lb n="2"/>mahāsenāpatisa mah<unclear>ā</unclear>talavarasa vāsiṭhīputasa pūkīyānaṁ mahākaṁdasirisa <lb n="3"/>bhayā mahāsenāpatisa mahātalavarasa viṇhusirisa mātā mahātalavari °apano <lb n="4"/>°ubhayakulaṁ parināmet<unclear>u</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">na</supplied> °atano °ubhayalokahitasukhanivāṇatha<supplied reason="omitted">nā</supplied>ya ca °imaṁ <lb n="5"/>selakhaṁbhaṁ patiṭhapitaṁ <space quantity="1" unit="character"/>mahārajasa sirivirapurisadatasa saṁva 6 vāpa 6 diva 10 </ab>
